    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="961300224">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-961300224" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-961300224" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="961300224">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1329593/">虾米</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-10-06</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">这书不太容易打分。作为史著来说，作者没有任何字句介入评论，这种写法不太多见。优点是避免向读者灌输先入为主的东西，缺陷就是比较散漫，抓不住重点。此外，此书编校不太理想。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

