        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/13196539/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/13196539/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/linyuxi/" class=" " title="林雨希">林雨希</a>
                (抬起头睁开眼　星星堆满天)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="13196539">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">读史其中一个用处就在于提醒吾人，事情可以匪夷所思到什么程度</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-06-05 20:20</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>读史其中一个用处就在于提醒吾人，事情可以匪夷所思到什么程度</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







